videos.description: Alondes Williams gets things started with a thunderous poster, then on the next possession Austin Reaves drives and skies for the slam. Finally, Reaves and Williams work in tandem to rock the rim.

videos.description: Brady Manek accounts for 22 of Oklahoma's 43 first-half points to help give the Sooners a 13-point lead at halftime.
